org.matsim.contrib.wagonSim.pt.router.deprecated

Class WagonSimRouterNetworkTravelDistutilityAndTravelTime2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.wagonSim.pt.router.deprecated.WagonSimRouterNetworkTravelDistutilityAndTravelTime2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatsimExtensionPoint, TravelTime, TransitTravelDisutility

    public class WagonSimRouterNetworkTravelDistutilityAndTravelTime2
extends Object
implements TransitTravelDisutility, TravelTime
    this class calculates disutility/traveltime completely independent. Thus, it might handle some parts different than the default TransitRouterNetworkTravelTimeAndDisutility, one the other hand some parts are very similar. Sometimes this is necessary because we e.g. do not want the first departure, when there is a later one which is not full.
    Author:
    droeder
